HEADWORD: Cineritious
<hw>Cin`er*i"tious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>cineritius</ets>, <ets>cinericius</ets>, fr. <ets>cinis</ets>
ashes.]</ety> <def>Like ashes; having the color of ashes, -- as the
